text: State Fair is a 1945 American musical movie directed by Walter Lang and starring Jeanne Crain, Dana Andrews, Dick Haymes, Vivian Blaine, Fay Bainter and Charles Winninger. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and won 1 Oscar for Best Original Song in 1946. It was the remake of the 1933 movie, which was released by Fox Film Corporation. == Other websites == * * Category:1945 musical movies Category:1940s American musical movies Category:Movies directed by Walter Lang Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies set in Iowa Category:Movies that won the Best Original Song Academy Award Category:Musicals by Rodgers and Hammerstein
